  "text": "(c) The Giesekus model for viscoelastic solutions [CITATION_1] , which includes a relaxation time, \u03bb G , and a polymer interaction term, the mobility parameter, a, gives the following implicit relationship for D/D 0 [CITATION_2] ;",
